OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist and fog lifting
OL,6,Fto leave warm sunny spells, especially
OL,7,Fin the east. Slowly turning cloudier
OL,8,Ffrom the west, with rain reaching west
OL,9,FCornwall in the afternoon, and a few
OL,10,Fshowers breaking out elsewhere.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome clear intervals in the
OL,13,Feast this evening, but rain edging
OL,14,Facross Cornwall, into parts of Devon,
OL,15,Fthen extending east to other areas
OL,16,Fduring the night. Temperatures holding
OL,17,Fup.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
