OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FLargely cloudy with a few
OL,6,Fspots of rain during the morning.
OL,7,FGradually brightening up from the west
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon. Becoming quite
OL,9,Fsunny across Cornwall. Feeling cooler
OL,10,Fcompared to Thursday.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FOccasional patchy rain and drizzle in
OL,14,Fplaces, but mostly dry albeit often
OL,15,Fcloudy. Cloud breaking at times to
OL,16,Fgive some sunshine. Temperatures
OL,17,Fcloser to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
